-- Secret Service Investigating Claims of Stolen Romney Tax Returns
-- B y   P h i l   M a t t i n g l y
-- 2012-09-05T23:11:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-05/secret-service-investigating-claims-of-stolen-romney-tax-returns.html
The U.S. Secret Service is
investigating reports that  Mitt Romney ’s tax returns have been
stolen and held for ransom, spokesman George Ogilvie said.  Federal officials are probing the claim from an anonymous
group that they broke into a PricewaterhouseCoopers office in
Nashville, Tennessee, and stole copies of the Republican
presidential candidate’s tax returns.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Phil Mattingly in Washington at 
